{"tid":1142333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一國附屬於另一國　沒有主權　稱為殖民地　即是現在香港情況","createTime":"2019-05-07T04:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T17:43:00.000Z","uid":47714,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d25c55c9cf61c9be2749030b7bcdbc53f64e8261","tid":1142333,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.wetalk.tw/thread-37976-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetalk.tw%2Fthread-37976-1-1.html&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=a459eb8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wetalk.tw/thread-37976-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實殖民地是很現代的譯法. 殖民地的存在很古老, 殖民主義的存在<br />\n很年輕. 殖民地的意思不過就是一個國家在另一個國家之下, 或者說,<br />\n一個國家附於另一個國家, 一個國家從屬另一個國家. 根據地位不同<br />\n或時代不同, 名稱有, 諸候國、內屬國、藩屬國、藩國、藩. 大英帝<br />\n國的殖民地部以前就是譯造理藩院."},{"pid":"9fefd2c5b55b4542eecf0680ae0d603fc4bad041","tid":1142333,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c51d503a1fda8e6de2d910a12dc50e15b832c67","tid":1142333,"uid":56015,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9fefd2c5b55b4542eecf0680ae0d603fc4bad041","tid":1142333,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"中國本來就係佔領香港"},{"pid":"353eac13ede0d9500d7a065478ea0cc6c885a4c3","tid":1142333,"uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"國家但冇主權<br />\n非主權國家 non-sovereign state / non-sovereign country<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thoughtco.com/country-state-and-nation-1433559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thoughtco.com%2Fcountry-state-and-nation-1433559&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b7758eac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thoughtco.com/country-state-and-nation-1433559</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/csYQaiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcsYQaiy.png&h=bab9b60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNon-Sovereign States<br />\nExamples include:<br />\nHong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indiastudychannel.com/forum/150056-What-is-the-difference-between-a-sovereign-country-and-non-sovereign.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiastudychannel.com%2Fforum%2F150056-What-is-the-difference-between-a-sovereign-country-and-non-sovereign.aspx&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ad4295ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiastudychannel.com/forum/150056-What-is-the-difference-between-a-sovereign-country-and-non-sovereign.aspx</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvshzMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvshzMi.png&h=03be45aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhat is the difference between a sovereign country and non sovereign country?<br />\nHow different from Hong Kong to other countries. Do Hong Kong is called a sovereign country?If a country is called as sovereign country then what are the guidelines they follow? Can you list these type of countries like Hong Kong in the world. I guess Taiwan one more country... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://dpxd.theletterdepot.com/legislatures-non-sovereign-countries\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdpxd.theletterdepot.com%2Flegislatures-non-sovereign-countries&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=095b05b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://dpxd.theletterdepot.com/legislatures-non-sovereign-countries</a><br />\nLegislatures of non-sovereign countries:<br />\nHong Kong   |   Legislative Council<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://avalon-linguistic.com/services/documents-translation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Favalon-linguistic.com%2Fservices%2Fdocuments-translation%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=6e98a2f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://avalon-linguistic.com/services/documents-translation/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NCqbEee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNCqbEee.png&h=e37da760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEnglish is official language in 67 countries and 27 non-sovereign countries such as Hong Kong, of the United Nations, the European Union, and of many other world and regional international organisations"},{"pid":"52b54504ba8c4f90f054560734af78b56751c1f2","tid":1142333,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3171ebfb58d8ac67971a811529e0f0a73af18f4","tid":1142333,"uid":60665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"英國管治時期叫殖民地，但其實大部份時間俾香港自治<br />\n而家聲稱香港自治，實質上係無自治權既中國殖民地"}]}